parameters:
(I did my best from the first day yesterday
because I had previous experience this time. I
moved around a lot and got tired, but it was to
catch Professor Hoffman.)

Amelia, you said you got some good information.
What kind of information is it?
スキット 表情 アメリ f 1

Yeah, I was planning to talk about it when
everyone gathered.

When I entered Professor Hoffman's workshop last
time, I was able to register the teleportation
stone that connects to the room.
スキット 表情 日和 f 32
スキット スライドイン 日和 f 左
Now we can investigate the room.
スキット 表情 アメリ f 1

Yeah. And also, I heard that Professor Hoffman
won't be going to the workshop today.
スキット 表情 アメリ f 5

He said he has preparations for class. It seems
like he's not always researching in the workshop
anyway.
If that's the case, it's a chance but...
スキット 表情 日和 f 41
スキット 表情 アメリ f 1
I think it's true because he said it himself.

...Let's go. We don't know when the next
opportunity will come.
I don't think we have much time left.
スキット 表情 日和 f 31

That's right. It has been some time since the
abnormality started happening.

gathering.
